data.description: Perfect Weekend Getaway Home. This charming home is located within the secure gates of Bear Valley Springs, a spectacular Gated community located in Tehachapi, CA. This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom 1,431 sq ft home is nestled up in the hills with Spectacular views! All appliances included, 2 car attached garage, in house laundry, picture window. This community is a town within itself, amenities include: Equestrian Center, Golf Course Campgrounds, Dog Park, Parks, Equestrian Trails & Hiking, Lakes, Nature Paths, Athletic Fields, Historical Preserve, Shooting Range, Tennis/Pickleball Courts, Recreation Center, Youth Sport Leagues, A 25 Yard Heated Pool & More! This cute home is a must see along with the private community!
